Here's my idea:<br>
<br>
Groupname: The Velious Crawlers<br>
Grouptype: Mini-raid/Crawl group<br>
Focus1: Fun and XP + making friends to raid with daily<br>
Focus2: Loot and money<br>
Target Zones: Tower of Frozen Shadow, Crystal Caverns with possible trips elsewhere dependant on the whim of the group.<br>
Raid dates: Weekdays if possible - not going to hold people strictly to playing every day, but the focus is on making friends in the same level range that play at the same time to group with on a daily basis.<br>
Raid time: 7pmCST(8pmEST) - 12amCST(1amEST) or whenever the group falls apart.<br>
Levelrange: 30-35 or so. Hopefully everyone will be around the same level so noone outlevels the others too fast.<br>
Ideal Group makeup: 1 SHM (me), 1 CLR or DRU/SHM, 1 ENC or BRD, 1 Pet Class (MAG, BST, NEC) or WIZ, 1 Tank class (WAR, PAL, SHD), 1 Damage Specialist (MNK, ROG, RNG)<br>
Groupalignment: We will be mostly a good/neut group. If you are a good race but evil class (NEC, SHD), please come up with a RP justification for joining. Pure evils will have to find another group - sorry.<br>
Let me know if you and who else is interested. Hopefully we can get this started on Monday Sep30<br>
